data.description:
Great home for primary residence or rental.  20 miles from Charlotte airport, 10 miles from Gastonia, and 30 miles from Hickory area. Price leaves plenty of room to start home ownership with equity. Needs updating and some minor repairs.

Primary Bedroom includes Primary Bathroom with separate shower and garden tub. Sunroom extends off the Living Room.

There is a well on the property that hasn't been used in several years. One outbuilding conveys with the property.  Two other outbuildings are for sale separately.  A singlewide mobile home used for storage is conveyed at no value.
